Tool / Component
Recommended Version / Constraint
Terraform CLI
~> 1.14 (i.e. 1.14.x) or latest 1.x release  
AzureRM provider
Use the latest 4.x (e.g. azurerm = "~> 4.0"). 4.x is stable and supported.  
TFLint
Latest stable (e.g. v0.60.0)  
TFLint Azure plugin (azurerm ruleset)
Latest plugin version (e.g. version = "0.30.0" in .tflint.hcl) â€” requires TFLint v0.46+.  
